    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and chop it roughly</p><p>Tear your <strong>basil leaves</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
