    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy salmon florentine</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>torn basil</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
